title: TF PUBLISHING -2022 Tropical Foliage Medium Monthly Planner
features: STYLISH AND CHIC: This monthly planner is made for productivity! Featuring a cover with a green and white tropical design, you’ll be motivated to plan and stay organized every day. It’s portable so you can bring it where your busy schedule takes you!

ORGANIZATION ESSENTIAL: Track your plans easily with this 6.5” x 8” planner! Covering January 2022 through December 2022, you’ll have all of your information in one convenient place. Bonus yearly overviews of 2022 and 2023 are included in the front.

STRAIGHTFORWARD DESIGN: This medium planner includes a monthly 2-page spread with a large calendar grid for daily plans. Planning pages and a notes section are also included to track your goals, to-do lists and more. You’ll never forget what’s important!

HIGH QUALITY: The textured pliable covers don’t just look good—they’re also durable! The planner lays flat whenever you use it and is protected wherever you take it. The sturdiness ensures that you’ll have it until you’ve finished the last monthly spread!

ECO-FRIENDLY: Since 1996, TF PUBLISHING has been one of the nation’s favorite shops for stationery products! Committed to the reduction of waste and use of plastics, our eco-conscious company recycles, composts, and produces “Goods Without Guilt”.
